data.revised_prompt: Create a high-quality, realistic image showing a cocktail known as 'Citrus Lavender Dream'. The drink is beautifully presented in a traditional coupe glass, showing a harmonious blend of soft lavender and vibrant sunlit citrus. Dressed with a lemon twist on the rim and a floating sprig of fresh lavender, all under gentle, diffused lighting that spreads a warm glow and gives the glass gentle reflections. The backdrop consists of a clean white canvas with discreet lavender tones to maintain attention on the drink. The overall setup exudes an inviting, tranquil atmosphere akin to a professional food photography. The ingredients include 2 oz Vodka, 1 oz Lavender Syrup, 0.5 oz Lemon Juice, and 0.5 oz Orange Juice. Avoid including any text, watermarks, and keep the background in soft focus.
